title: Qdoba company-owned restaurant sales from 2011 to 2018
summary: In general Sales in million U.S. dollars has fallen over the Year.
Sales in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2013 to 2017, and lastly slightly decreasing from 2017 to 2018.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Sales in million U.S. dollars, about 436.56 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Sales in million U.S. dollars about 192.62 was reached at Year 2018
